Cell["\<\
Q3 functions that are useful to construct a linear combination of unitary \
operators.\
\>", "TechNoteCaption",
 CellID->1909264679,ExpressionUUID->"3fca5bd0-de6a-4406-a2eb-4db45e6349e8"],

